// Typography
section.container.typography-section
	.row
		main.content.col-sm-7
			h2.section-title Typography
			a.anchor-link#typography
			.intro-copy.link-underline
				p Fonts are stored as SASS <em>mixins</em> so they can be used anywhere in the .scss files without fear of cascading styles overriding them.
				p You can easily implement the mixin by targeting a specific .title, or other, class as seen in the following lines:

				pre: code.
					.archives-page {
						.title {@include sans-lg}
					}

				p Font sizes were determined by the design and with the major second modular scale mainly for responsive sizes (1.125). See <a href="http://www.modularscale.com" target="_blank">www.modularscale.com</a>.

		aside.sidebar.sidebar--info.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
			h3.sidebar-section-title References
			ul
				li.sidebar-item.sidebar-highlight
					a(href="https://sass-guidelin.es/#mixins" target="_blank")
						h4.sidebar-item-title SASS mixins
						.info sass-guidelin.es/#mixins
				li.sidebar-item.sidebar-highlight
					a(href="http://www.modularscale.com/?2.4&rem&1.125&web&text" target="_blank")
						h4.sidebar-item-title Serif Scale (base 2.4rem, 1.125, major second)
						.info modularscale.com
				li.sidebar-item.sidebar-highlight
					a(href="http://www.modularscale.com/?3&rem&1.125&web&text" target="_blank")
						h4.sidebar-item-title Sans Scale (base 3rem, 1.125, major second)
						.info modularscale.com
					
	// Typefaces
	.typeface
		.row.type-title-wrapper
			hr
			.col-sm-10.large-serif-title-type.type-title Large Serif Title
			.col-sm-2
				.show-code Show Code
					.icon-down-arrow
		.row
			.col-md-5
				.type-details
					|Typeface: Freight Text
					br
					|Weight: Bold
					br
					|Maximum Font Size: 6.158rem
					br
					|Maximum Line Height: 6.738rem

			.col-md-7
				pre.type: code.
					@mixin serif-lg {
						font-family: $serif;
						font-weight: 700;
						line-height: 1.1;
						font-size: 4.865rem;
						@include respond-to(break2) {
							font-size: 5.474rem;			
						}
						@include respond-to(fullwidth) {
							font-size: 6.158rem;
					}

